QueryText: Farmer asked the query regarding Marssonina leaf blotch in apple
KccAns: it is advised to the farmer spray any micronutrient like agromin or microvit 400g-600g200 litres of water after  a gap of three days spray any zinc based fungicide  Mancozeb 75 WP 300 g   or Ziram 27 SC   600 ml   or Zineb 75 WP  300 g  or Ziram  80 WP  200 g  in 100 litres of water

QueryText: Farmer asked the query regarding spray schedule in apple for problem of letical blotch and  Marssonina leaf blotch
KccAns: t is advised to the farmer Two to three sprays of Ca and boron is required in fruits for maintenance of firmness Even after its availability in the soil it is not available to the apple fruits in appropriate quantities because of its very slow mobility The ideal time of Ca and boron sprays in apple is right from Pea size to 30-45 days prior to harvesting of fruits It should be in the form of Calcium chloride 300g per 100 ltrs of water along with Boric acid  15 g per ltr of waterand care should be taken Dont mix fungicide because Mixing calcium chloride with commercial fungicide formulations results in very slow penetration of calcium into apple fruits after a gap of 3 days of spraying calcium spray one of the following fungicide Mancozeb 75 WP 300 g  or Ziram 27 SC   600 ml  or Zineb 75 WP 300 g or Ziram  80 WP  200 g or Chlorothalonil 75 WP 150 g in 100 ltrs of water

QueryText: Farmer asked the query regarding Marssonina leaf blotch in apple
KccAns: It is advised to the farmer spray Mancozeb 75 WP 300 g    or Ziram 27 SC   600 ml     or Zineb 75 WP  300 g or Ziram  80 WP  200 g  or Chlorothalonil 75 WP 150 g or Propineb 70 WP    300 g  In case rainy weather hampers VII FD II spray Difenaconazole 25 EC  30 ml or Trifloxystrobin 25  Tebuconazole 50  75 WG  40g in 100 ltrs of water

QueryText: REGARDING NECROTIC LEAF BLOTCHMARSSONINA LEAF BLOTCH
KccAns: SPRAY MULTINUTRIENT  AGROMIN MULTIPLEX MICROVIT  400-600 GRAM PER 200 LITRE OF WATER    AFTER  A GAP OF 3 DAYS GO FOR APPLICATION    ZINC BASED FUNGICIDE  ZIRAM 80 WP 200 GRAM OR MANCOZEB 75 WP 300 GRAM OR ZIRAM 27 W 600 ML OR ZINEB 75 WP 300 GRAM OR PROPINEB 70 WP 300 GRAM    SPRAY THIOPHANATE METHYL 50 GRAM100 LITRE OF WATER OR DODINE 75 GRAM  100 LITRE OF WATER  FOR MARSSONINA LEAF BLOTCH     COLLECT AND BURN FALLEN LEAVES  FIELD SANITATION IS MUST
